ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 208, New Brunswick
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 208 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK, with respect to the ice storm that occurred on January 24 and January 25, 2017.
